ger_(baseball)" title="Manager (baseball)">Manager</a></b></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><b>Born:</b> <span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1918-08-30</span>)</span>August 30, 1918<br /><a href="/wiki/San_Diego,_California" class="mw-redirect" title="San Diego, California">San Diego, California</a>, U.S.</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><b>Died:</b> July 5, 2002<span style="display:none">(2002-07-05)</span> (aged&#160;83)<br /><a href="/wiki/Inverness,_Florida" title="Inverness, Florida">Inverness, Florida</a>, U.S.</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><div class="ib-baseball-bio-batsthrows"><div><b>Batted:</b> Left</div><div><b>Threw:</b> Right</div></div></td></tr><tr style="background-color:#DCDCDC;color:#000000;"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">MLB debut</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data">April 20,&#160;1939,&#160;for the&#160;Boston Red Sox</td></tr><tr style="background-color:#DCDCDC;color:#000000;"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">Last MLB appearance</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data">September 28,&#160;1960,&#160;for the&#160;Boston Red Sox</td><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1218072481"></tr><tr style="background-color:#DCDCDC;color:#000000;"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">MLB statistics</th></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="text-align:right; width:50%; padding-right:0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/Batting_average_(baseball)" title="Batting average (baseball)">Batting average</a></th><td class="infobox-data" style="width:50%; padding-left:0.5em;">.344</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="text-align:right; width:50%; padding-right:0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/Hit_(baseball)" title="Hit (baseball)">Hits</a></th><td class="infobox-data" style="width:50%; padding-left:0.5em;">2,654</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="text-align:right; width:50%; padding-right:0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/Home_run" title="Home run">Home runs</a></th><td class="infobox-data" style="width:50%; padding-left:0.5em;">521</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="text-align:right; width:50%; padding-right:0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/Run_batted_in" title="Run batted in">Runs batted in</a></th><td class="infobox-data" style="width:50%; padding-left:0.5em;">1,839</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="text-align:right; width:50%; padding-right:0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/On-base_percentage" title="On-base percentage">On-base percentage</a></th><td class="infobox-data" style="width:50%; padding-left:0.5em;">.482</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="text-align:right; width:50%; padding-right:0.5em;">Managerial record</th><td class="infobox-data" style="width:50%; padding-left:0.5em;">273–364</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="text-align:right; width:50%; padding-right:0.5em;">Winning&#160;%</th><td class="infobox-data" style="width:50%; padding-left:0.5em;">.429</td></tr><tr style="display:none"><th colspan="2">
</th></tr><tr style="background-color:#DCDCDC;color:#000000;"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">Teams</th></tr><tr class="ib-baseball-bio-teams"><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data"><b>As player</b>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Boston_Red_Sox" title="Boston Red Sox">Boston Red Sox</a> (<a href="/wiki/1939_Major_League_Baseball_season" title="1939 Major League Baseball season">1939</a>–<a href="/wiki/1942_Major_League_Baseball_season" title="1942 Major League Baseball season">1942</a>, <a href="/wiki/1946_Major_League_Baseball_season" title="1946 Major League Baseball season">1946</a>–<a href="/wiki/1960_Major_League_Baseball_season" title="1960 Major League Baseball season">1960</a>)</li></ul>
<p><b>As manager</b>
</p>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Texas_Rangers_(baseball)" title="Texas Rangers (baseball)">Washington Senators / Texas Rangers</a> (<a href="/wiki/1969_Major_League_Baseball_season" title="1969 Major League Baseball season">1969</a>–<a href="/wiki/1972_Major_League_Baseball_season" title="1972 Major League Baseball season">1972</a>)</li></ul>
</td></tr><tr style="background-color:#DCDCDC;color:#000000;"><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header">Career highlights and awards</th></tr><tr class="ib-baseball-bio-highlights"><td colspan="2" class="infobox-full-data">
<ul><li>19× <a href="/wiki/Major_League_Baseball_All-Star_Game" title="Major League Baseball All-Star Game">All-Star</a> (<a href="/wiki/1940_Major_League_Baseball_All-Star_Game" title="1940 Major League Baseball All-Star Game">1940</a>–<a href="/wiki/1942_Major_League_Baseball_All-Star_Game" title="1942 Major League Baseball All-Star Game">1942</a>, <a href="/wiki/1946_Major_League_Baseball_All-Star_Game" title="1946 Major League Baseball All-Star Game">1946</a>–<a href="/wiki/1951_Major_League_Baseball_All-Star_Game" title="1951 Major League Baseball All-Star Game">1951</a>, <a href="/wiki/1953_Major_League_Baseball_All-Star_Game" title="1953 Major League Baseball All-Star Game">1953</a>–<a href="/wiki/1960_Major_League_Baseball_All-Star_Game_(second_game)" title="1960 Major League Baseball All-Star Game (second game)">1960²</a>)</li>
